<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/582586-hey-i-got-this-book-and-i-want-to-know-if">Hey, I got this book and I want to know if it is worth reading. Is it?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_582586'><a id="like_count_community_question_582586" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/582586?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">1 like</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F9475.Midnight_for_Charlie_Bone">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
