  <span id="freeText4981967179452382106" style="display:none">I'm rereading this series before giving away the books to my new younger brother. This book was even more fun than I remember it being! It's about a formerly unexceptional boy named Charlie Bone who suddenly finds he can hear people in photographs. His life rapidly changes and he now has to go to an old school for children with exceptional abilities in art, music, or drama, which also teaches children with special powers like talking to animals and telekinesis. Adventures, mysteries, friendships and villains await him inside and outside the doors of Bloor's Academy.</span>
