<span id="freeTextContainer6741048206643144568">I read this book at the encouragement of a young person in my house, and I’m glad I did! It was a fun and unputdownable read, and the ending had me reaching for book 2 in the series. This series is very appropriately marketed to middle grade readers, and I tried to keep that in mind as I read it—it has just the right level of intrigue for a 4th-6th grader, in my opinion. </span>

          </span>
